    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches, some fading paint, and a few small dents. Inside, the upholstery has visible stains and significant wear on the front seats. All mechanical systems are functional, though the car shows signs of heavy regular use.",
      "price": 24000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, indicating that major repairs or a full overhaul are likely necessary. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust, multiple dents, and fading paint, while the interior has significant tearing and non-functional electronics. It is best suited as a dedicated project car or for salvageable parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an uncompromising level of care and a flawless aesthetic profile. For the discerning client who demands a specimen of unrivaled caliber, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine automobile.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been pampered since day one and is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like a dream! I've taken such good care of it, but it's time for a new home. You really have to see this one in person to believe how perfect it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, maintained to an exacting standard. The S54B32 power plant remains in peak factory specification, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS system. The rod bearings and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for this chassis\u2014have been proactively addressed with documented precision. Suspension kinematics are preserved via fresh bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring the original balance of the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup. This example exhibits zero discernible parasitic loss in the drivetrain and retains its original factory paint depth. A true turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No accidents. Original paint. Interior as new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved since day one. The exterior finish glows with a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the premium leather seats are supple without any bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records to prove it. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. It is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, reflects a standard of care that is exceedingly rare in the pre-owned market. Mechanically, the vehicle remains indistinguishable from its factory-original state, having undergone an exhaustive certification process to ensure unrivaled performance. This is a singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality specimen of uncompromising caliber.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute stunner. It's in such incredible shape, you'd honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I've babied this car since day one, and it truly shows in every single detail. It's been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy that 'new car' feeling. Come say hi and take a look\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a masterclass in JDM engineering, preserved in showroom condition. Power is derived from the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, featuring flawless compression and its original sequential forced-induction system. The drivetrain utilizes the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains perfectly balanced, riding on an untouched double-wishbone suspension setup with all OEM bushings and linkages intact. With zero aftermarket interference, this vehicle retains its factory-spec intercooler, vacuum lines, and ECU mapping, representing a true turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 49250.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_8",
